---
import { internalPath, siteConfig } from "../../site-config";
import { STEWERSHIP_LEGAL_OPERATOR } from "../../lib/stewardship-legal";

const termsHref = internalPath("terms-of-service");
const phone = siteConfig.phoneDisplay?.trim();
const tel = siteConfig.phoneE164?.trim();
const hasPhone = Boolean(phone && tel);
---

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="legal-updated"><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 30, 2026</p>

<div class="legal-disclaimer-box">
  <strong>Community education only</strong>
  These pages are neighbor-stewardship reference materials. They are not paid dispatch, contractor
  matching, or insurance advice. See our <a href={termsHref}>Terms of Service</a> for full disclaimers.
</div>

<p>
  <strong>Operator:</strong> {STEWERSHIP_LEGAL_OPERATOR}<br />
  <strong>Website:</strong> {siteConfig.canonicalOrigin}
  {hasPhone ? (
    <>
      <br />
      <strong>Volunteer reference desk:</strong>{" "}
      <a href={`tel:${tel!.replace(/^\+/, "")}`}>{phone}</a>
    </>
  ) : null}
</p>

<h2>1. Overview</h2>
<p>
  This Privacy Policy explains how we handle limited information when you visit our community
  stewardship pages. These materials support voluntary neighbor education about housing upkeep topics
  (water, exterior, plumbing reference notes). We do <strong>not</strong> operate a contractor
  marketplace, paid dispatch desk, or lead-sales program on this site.
</p>

<h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Basic technical data: IP address, browser type, device, pages visited, referring URL</li>
  <li>Cookies and analytics (e.g., page views) used to understand readership and improve clarity</li>
  <li>
    Information you choose to share if you contact a volunteer reference desk (e.g., email or message
    content)
  </li>
</ul>
<p>
  We do <strong>not</strong> collect information for commercial telemarketing, insurance sales, or
  third-party data brokerage on these pages.
</p>

<h2>3. How we use information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Operate and secure the website</li>
  <li>Measure aggregate readership (analytics)</li>
  <li>Respond to good-faith volunteer or fellowship inquiries when you contact us directly</li>
  <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. How we share information</h2>
<p>
  We may share limited data with hosting or analytics providers that help run the site. We do{" "}
  <strong>not</strong> sell personal information. We do <strong>not</strong> share visitor data with
  home-service contractors for paid handoffs from these stewardship pages.
</p>

<h2>5. Illustrative content on ZIP pages</h2>
<p>
  Some pages show educational anchors, stress indexes, or charts derived from public-style context.
  These are <strong>illustrative planning notes only</strong> — not engineering reports, insurer
  findings, bids, or government determinations.
</p>

<h2>6. Your choices</h2>
<p>
  You may use browser controls to limit cookies where available.
  {hasPhone ? (
    <>
      {" "}
      Privacy questions may be directed to the volunteer reference desk at{" "}
      <a href={`tel:${tel!.replace(/^\+/, "")}`}>{phone}</a>.
    </>
  ) : (
    <> Privacy questions may be directed through fellowship contact channels listed on this site.</>
  )}
</p>

<h2>7. Data retention</h2>
<p>
  We retain information only as long as needed for site security, aggregate analytics, or legal
  compliance, then delete or de-identify where appropriate.
</p>

<h2>8. Security</h2>
<p>
  We use reasonable safeguards. No Internet transmission is 100% secure.
</p>

<h2>9. Children</h2>
<p>
  These materials are intended for general community readers. We do not knowingly collect information
  from children under 13.
</p>

<h2>10. Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this policy. The &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date will change when we do.</p>

<h2>11. Contact</h2>
<p>
  {STEWERSHIP_LEGAL_OPERATOR}
  {hasPhone ? (
    <>
      <br />
      Volunteer reference desk: <a href={`tel:${tel!.replace(/^\+/, "")}`}>{phone}</a>
    </>
  ) : null}
</p>
